<LI><I><FONT SIZE=+1>Control of Nonholonomic Systems</FONT></I></LI>

<LI><I><FONT SIZE=+1>Discrete-time Sliding Modes</FONT></I></LI>

<LI><I><FONT SIZE=+1>Sliding Mode Control of Distributed Parameter Systems</FONT></I></LI>

<LI><I><FONT SIZE=+1>Sliding Mode Control of Hybrid Systems</FONT></I></LI>

<LI><I><FONT SIZE=+1>Multiresolutional Sliding Mode Control</FONT></I></LI>
</UL>

